Changes to MTF

2021-Feb-17

  • Changed Expense Report/Report Item/Reciept Data Collection for the first 3 tabs (and linked views) to filter to the current user

2021-Feb-16

  • Advances Tab & Request Form
  • Advance Approval Process

2021-Feb-11

  • Added a Payments Tab and Form - Will be used to mark reimbursements as paid out.
  • Added Cash Account to Expense report with label (Paid From) - used only when paying out reimbursements
  • Added 'Person - Profile' as Staff on Expense Report - so Approvers know who submitted the report
  • Modified the Add Report form:
    • Record rule to set 'Staff' to the current user ('User Person' data collection)
    • Modified the Submit rule to route to 'View Expense Report' page which has an option to submit.

2021-Feb-03

[Nathan]

  • Change the Report Items tab to only show unclaimed report items.
    • Created a new data colllection 'Report Items - No Report'
    • Changed the Grid in Report Items Tab to the new DC
  • Changed Reciepts Tab to only show Reciepts for Unsubmitted Report Items
    • Added Data Collections:
      • Expense Report - Not Draft (status: not 'draft')
      • Report Items - Unsubmitted (report not in dc above)
      • Reciepts - Unsubmitted (Report Item in dc above)
      • Changed Reciepts tab to use Reciepts - Unsubmitted DC
  • Changed Expense Report Status Options (We need more fore the full appproval process)
    - Approved > TL Approved
    + QX Approved
    + Paid
    - Added data collections for Expense Report Statuses ('Expense Report - Submitted', 'Expense Report - TL Approved', 'Expense Report - QX Approved'
  • Started building a TL Approval Page
    • It is too complex to do in an approval taks 
    • (Will need pages for QX Approval and Field Finance Payment)
